                            <comment id="14431789" author="ltheussl" created="Tue, 15 Feb 2011 01:19:24 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The anchors are inserted externally of doxia by the SiteRenderer&apos;s SiteRendererSink, the doxia parser behaves correctly, see &lt;a href=&quot;http://svn.apache.org/viewvc?rev=1070789&amp;amp;view=rev&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;r1070789&lt;/a&gt;. Unfortunately, the documentation is misleading, as using the site plugin effectively leads to anchor creation. I need to check where/how to document this properly.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14431858" author="sebb@apache.org" created="Tue, 15 Feb 2011 05:43:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;In that case. there is a bug in the SiteRenderer - it should not add the extra anchors. Issue created.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
